CJD OR NVCJD DIAGNOSIS - USA (02)
=================================
[see
CJD or nvCJD diagnosis - USA 970410172030]
[1]
Date: Sat, 12 Apr 1997 11:10:28 -0400
From: Meryl Nass <mnass@igc.apc.org>
Subject: ?Parent with CJD/nvCJD
I agree with the author as to the minimal likelihood of getting these
diagnoses made in the current climate of health funding. Surveillance
is falling down (it was often paid for in the past by cost-shifting) in
the current system; probably it's another argument for a single-payer
plan.
---
M. Nass, M.D.
